narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, best run department at Yale but expect a lot from "beginners" (people who are actually starting out v. people who have a small background)
Yes. Low difficulty intro course in Spanish, but you definitely learn a lot.
Spanish 110 is a good intro course, although it may seem hard at first for those that have never had Spanish or took it in high school. I would recommend this to anyone wanting to take Spanish.
I would only if he/she actually wants to learn Spanish and not only just to fulfill the language requirements. You must be dedicated to the course in order to do well.
